Ontology:               Smart Home Environments Ontology (eCare@Home) (SmartEnv)
DISO directory:         smart-environments/smart-homes/SmartEnv
Ontology files:         SmartEnvMerged.ttl (plus README.md recording provenance)
Obtained from:          http://ecareathome-ontology.mpi.aass.oru.se/ (per the
                        local README.md: the master ontology SmartEnv.owl and
                        its 8 imported component pattern ontologies were merged
                        with Protege into SmartEnvMerged.ttl). The canonical
                        identifier https://w3id.org/smartenvironment/smartenv.owl
                        redirects (302) to the same host.
